>Ok, found a VIN number 507 5XX
>Two sources said it's a 60, and two sources said 59.

From Doliwa:

   August    1959  501 507  Hand brake and gear shift moved. 
                   507 5xx  Your Bus
24 September 1959  511 907  Transmission changed.
30 September 1959  514 885  Begin model year 1960. 

From that I'd say it was built mid-September 1959 as one of the
last 1959 models.

